  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survive the chaos!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dodge massive falling lava rocks as they shatter the ground beneath you in this intense survival challenge. Designed in <strong>Unreal Engine 5</strong> and powered by the <strong>Chaos physics system</strong>, the environment dynamically breaks apart, forcing you to adapt and stay on solid ground for as long as possible. Can you outlast the destruction?</p>",
